hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
4606,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nabuwat mein sirf ''mubashshiraat'' baqi reh gaey hain.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : mubashshiraat se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achey khuwab .'' Bukhari ."
4607,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ata bin Yasar ki riwayat ke hawaley se ye izafa kya hai : ''(wo khaab ( jisey musalman shakhs dekhta hai, ya uski khatir ( kisi doosrey shakhs ko) dikhaya jata hai.'' rawahu Malik."
4608,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achey khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4609,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne mujhey khuwab mein dekha to usney mujhey hi dekha kyonkey shetan mera roop nahin dhaar sakta. '' muttafaq aleh.
4610,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney mujhey dekha to usney haq (haqiqat mein mujhey ( dekha .'' muttafaq aleh."
4611,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney mujhey khaab mein dekha to wo mujhey an-qareeb haalatebedaarii mein bhi dekhega aur shetan meri surat ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta.'' muttafaq aleh."
4612,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achhey khuwab Allah ki taraf se hain, aur burey khuwab shetan ki taraf se hain, jab tum mein se koi pasandida chiz dekhey to wo uska izhar usi se karey jisey wo pasand karta hai, aur agar koi naa-pasandida khuwab dekhey to wo uskey shar se aur shetan ke shar se Allah ki panah talab karey aur teen baar (apni baain janib) thuthkaarey aur uskey mutalliq kisi se baat na karey, is tarah wo uskey liye Muzar (nuksandeh) nahin hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4613,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi eik naa-pasandida khuwab dekhey to wo apney baain taraf teen baar thookey aur teen baar shetan se Allah ki panah talab karey aur wo jis pehlu par tha usey badal ley.'' rawahu Muslim."
4614,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab (qiyamat ka ( zamana qarib aa jaeyga to qarib nahin ke momin ka khuwab jhoota hoga, momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaliswan hissey hai, aur jo chiz nabuwat se ho wo jhooti nahin hoti.'' muttafaq aleh. Muhammad bin Sireen bayan kartey hain, main kehta hun : khuwab teen qism ke hain : nafsiyaati khayal, shetan ka darana aur Allah ki taraf se bashaarat. lihaza jo shakhs koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhey to wo usey kisi se bayan na karey, aur khada ho kar Namaz padhey. unhoney farmaya : wo khuwab mein toq dekhney ko napasand kartey they aur paaon mein bediyan unhen pasand thin, aur kaha jata hai ke bediyon se murad Deen par Sabit qadmi hai."
4615,"Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : isey Qatada, Yunus, Hasheem aur Abu Hilal ne ibne Sireen ki sanad se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Yunus ne kaha : main (فی القید) ke alfaz ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees se shumar karta hun. aur Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : mujhey malum nahin ke wo alfaz aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hain ya ibne Sireen ke hain aur isi jaisi eik riwayat mein hai aur usney ''aap napasand kartey toq . . . . .'' se aakhir hadees tak ke alfaz hadees mein dakhil kiye hain. muttafaq aleh."
4616,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, maine khuwab mein dekha hai ke mera sar kaat diya gaya hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye aur farmaya : ''jab shetan kisi se uski neend mein kheley to wo logon ko na bataey.'' rawahu Muslim."
4617,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine eik raat khuwab mein dekha ke ham Aqba bin Raafe ke ghar mein hain aur hamarey paas ibne Taab ki khajuren laee gaeen, maine ye taaweel ki ke duniya mein hamarey liye rifat (bulandi) hai aur aakhirat mein nek anjam ke taur par hamarey liye hai, aur hamara Deen yaqinan kamil aur behtar hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
4618,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine khuwab mein dekha ke main Makka se khajuron ki sarzameen ki taraf hijrat kar raha hun, mera khayal tha ke wo yamaama hai ya hijr hai, lekin wo (sarzameen) Madina hai jis ka naam yasrab tha, aur maine apney usi khuwab mein dekha ke maine apni talwaar hilaai to uska wast (beech) toot gaya, us se murad wo hai jo mominon ko ghazwae uhad mein takleef uthani padi , phir maine dobara usey hilaya to wo apni pehli haalat se bhi behtar ho gaee , us se murad wo hai jo Allah Taala ne (Makka ki) Fateh ata farmaee aur mominon ko ikhatta kar diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
4619,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isi beech mein ke main so raha tha ke mujh par zamin ke khazaney pesh kiye gaey, merey haath mein soney ke do kangan rakh diye gaey to wo mujh par giraan guzrey, phir meri taraf ""wahi'' ki gaee ke main unhen phunk maarun , maine phunk maari to wo dono jatey rahey, maine unki ye tabeer ki ke is se murad wo do jhootey shakhs hain, main unke darmiyan hun, eik (Aswad Ansaa) Sanaa se aur eik (Musailma Kazaab) yamaama se.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''un dono mein se eik Musailma yamaama ka rehney wala aur Ansaa Sanaa ka rehney wala.'' lekin maine ye riwayat saheehain mein nahin pai aur sahibul jaame ne isey Tirmizi se riwayat kiya hai. muttafaq aleh aur Tirmizi."
4620,"Hazrat Umme-Ala Ansaariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine khuwab mein Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye eik behta chashma dekha, maine uska tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uska amal hai jo uskey liye jari kiya gaya hai.'' Bukhari ."
4621,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz padh letey to aap apna rukhe-anwar hamari taraf kar letey aur farmatey : ''aaj raat tum mein se kisi ne khuwab dekha hai? '' raawi bayan kartey hain, agar kisi ne dekha hota to wo usey bayan kar deta, aur aap jo Allah chahta , uski tabeer bayan farma detey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz ham se puchha : ''kya tum mein se kisi ne khuwab dekha hai?'' ham ne arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' lekin maine aaj raat do aadmi dekhay, wo merey paas aaye to unhoney mujhey haathon se pakda aur mujhey arze-muqaddas ki taraf ley gaey, wahan eik aadmi betha hua tha aur eik khada tha, uskey haath mein lohey ka eik tukda tha, wo usko uskey jabdey mein dakhil karta tha, aur usko uski guddi tak cheer deta tha, phir wo isi tarah doosrey jabdey ke sath karta tha, aur itney mein ye (pehla) jabdaa theek ho jata tha, aur wo us amal ko dohraata tha, maine puchha : ye kya hai? un dono ne kaha : (aagey) chalo, ham chaley yahan tak ke ham eik aadmi ke paas aaye jo chit letaa hua tha aur eik aadmi chhota ya bada pathar liye uskey sarhaaney khada tha aur wo uskey sath uskey sar ko kuchal raha tha, jab wo usey maarta tha, to patthar ludhak jata tha, wo usey leney jata lekin uskey wapis aaney se pehley uska sar phir theek ho jata tha, aur wo aadmi uskey sath phir wesey hi karta tha aur ye amal jari rehta hai, maine kaha : ye kya hai? un dono ne kaha : (aagey) chalen, ham chaley yahan tak ke tandoor jaisey surakh ke paas aaye jis ka ooper ka hissa tang hai jabkey uska nichlaa hissey khula hai, uskey nichey aag jal rahi thi, jab wo ooper uthti to is mein mojud afrad bhi ooper buland hotey yahan tak ke aisey lagta ke wo us se nikal jaeyngey, aur jab wo bujh jati to wo is mein wapis aa jatey aur is mein mard aur aurten barahna (nangey) then, maine kaha, ye kya hai? un dono ne kaha : (aagey) chalen, ham chaley yahan tak ke ham khoon ki nehar par pahunchey, wahan nehar ke samney patthar hain, wo shakhs jo nehar mein hai jab wo bahar nikalney ka irada karta tha to bahar kinarey par khada aadmi uskey munh par patthar phainktaa aur usey apni pehli jagah par pahuncha deta hai, wo jab bhi nikalney ke liye aata tha phir wo uskey munh par patthar maarta hai to wo wapis wahin chala jata tha, maine kaha : ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : (aagey) chalen , ham chaley yahan tak ke ham sar-sabz (hare) aur shadab baagh mein pahunch gaey, us main eik bada darkht tha aur uskey taney ke paas eik Umar-raseeda (buzurg) shakhs aur kuchh bachhey they, aur darkht ke qarib eik aadmi tha uskey aagey aag thi jisey wo jala raha tha, wo mujhey darkht par ley gaey, unhoney mujhey darkht ke wast (beech) main eik ghar mein dakhil kar diya, maine us se khoobsurat ghar kabhi nahin dekha, is mein boodhey mard , nojawan , khawatin aur bachchey they, phir wo mujhey wahan se bahar ley aaye aur darkht par ley chadhey , aur mujhey us se bhi achhey aur behtar ghar mein ley gaey, is mein boodhey aur jawan they, maine un dono se kaha : tum raat bhar mujhey liye phirtey rahey ho, lihaza maine jo kuchh dekha uskey mutalliq mujhey bataao? unhoney kaha : ji haan ! raha wo shakhs jis ko aapney dekha ke uskey jabdey ko chira ja raha tha to wo jhoota shakhs tha, wo jhoot bayan karta tha, phir us se naqal kiya jata tha yahan tak ke wo aafaaq tak pahunch jata, aapney jo dekha wo roze-qiyamat tak uskey sath kiya jaeyga, wo aadmi jo aapney dekha ke uska sar kuchla ja raha tha, ye wo shakhs tha jisney Quran ka ilm seekha lekin usney raat ka qiyam na kiya aur na din ke waqt uskey mutabiq amal kiya, aapney jo dekha uskey sath ye sulook qiyamat tak jari rahega , aapney jinhen surakh mein dekha wo zina kaar they, aapney jisey nehar mein dekha tha wo sood khor tha, aapney darkht ke taney ke sath jis buzurg shakhs ko dekha wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) they aur unke ird-gird jo bachchey they wo logon ki aulad thi, jo shakhs aag jala raha tha wo jahannam ka darogha Maalik tha, aap jis pehley ghar mein dakhil huey they wo aam mominon ka ghar tha, raha ye ghar to ye shuhda ka ghar hai, main Jibrael hun aur ye mekael hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna sar uthaeyn , jab maine sar uthaya to merey ooper badalon ki manind tha, un dono ne kaha : ye aap ki manzil hai, maine kaha : mujhey chhod do , main apni manzil mein dakhil ho jaaun unhoney kaha : abhi aap ki umr baqi hai jo aapney mukammal nahin ki, jab aap usey mukammal kar lengey to aap apni manzil mein dakhil ho jaeyngey.'' Bukhari. aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ''nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khuwab mein Madina dikhai dena'' ( Harame-Madina wale baab mein) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4622,"Hazrat Abu Rizeen Aqeeli bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaliswan hissey hai, jab tak wo usko bayan nahin karta to wo perindey ke paaon par hai, lekin jab wo usey bayan kar deta hai to wo waqey ho jata hai.'' aur mera khayal hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kisi aziz dost ya aql-mand shakhs ke siwa kisi aur se bayan na karo.'' Tirmizi. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : farmaya : ''jab tak khuwab ki tabeer na ki jaey to wo perindey ke paaon par hota hai, lekin jab uski tabeer bayan ki jati hai to wo waqey ho jata hai.'' aur mera khayal hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kisi aziz dost ya aql-mand shakhs ke siwa kisi aur se bayan na kar.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4623,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Warqa bin Nofal ke barey mein puchha gaya to Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tasdeeq kar di thi lekin wo aap ke aelane-nabuwat se pehley faut ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey mujhey khuwab mein dikhaya gaya is par safed kapdey they, aur agar wo jahannami hota to is par koi aur libas hota.'' (rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi)."
4624,"Hazrat ibne Khuzaima bin Sabit apney chacha Abu Khuzaima se bayan kartey hain, unhoney khuwab dekha ke usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki peshani par sajda kiya hai, usney aap ko bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski khatir let gaey aur farmaya : ''apna khuwab sachcha kar dikhaao.'' usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki peshani par sajda kiya. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah). aur ham Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''goya wo meezaan (tarazu) hai jo aasman se nazil hui.'' (baabe-manaaqib Abi Bakr aur umr (Raziallahu anhu)) mein zikr karengey."
4625,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba se aksar yun farmaya kartey they : ''kya tum mein se kisi ne khuwab dekha hai?'' wo aap sey, jo Allah chahta , bayan karte, isi tarah aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz hamein farmaya : ''do aaney waley merey paas aaye unhoney mujhey uthaya aur unhoney mujhey kaha : chalo , aur main unke sath chala.'' aur phir pahli fasal mein mazkura hadees mukammal taur par bayan ki, aur is mein izafa hai jo ke hadees mazkur mein nahin, aur wo ye hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham eik intehai sar sabz (hare) baagh mein aaye , is mein mausame-bahar ke tamam phool , aur baagh ke wast (beech) main eik taweel aadmi tha aur uskey daraazi qad ki wajeh se main uska sar nahin dekh sakta tha, jabkey us aadmi ke ird-gird bahut se bachchey hain, jinhen maine (itni kasrat mein pehley) hergiz nahin dekha, maine un dono aadmiyon se kaha : ye kon hain? aap farmatey hain, unhoney mujhey kaha : (aagey) chalen ! ham chaley aur eik badey baagh ke paas pahunchey, maine us se bada aur us se ziyada behtar baagh kabhi nahin dekha.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey hain : ''unhoney mujhey kaha : is mein ooper chadho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham is mein chadhey aur eik shehar mein pahunchey jiski taamir is tarah hui thi ke uski eik eent soney ki aur eik eent chaandi ki thi, ham shehar ke darwazey par pahunchey aur darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, aur wo hamarey liye khol diya gaya to ham is mein dakhil ho gaey, ham is mein kuchh aadmiyon se miley unka aadha dhad itna khoobsurat tha ke tum ne kabhi nahin dekha hoga aur unka aadha dhad is qadr qabeeh (badsurat) tha ke tum ne kabhi nahin dekha hoga, un dono ne unhen kaha : jaao aur us nehar mein gir jaao.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wahan eik chodi nehar jari thi goya uska pani khalis safed hai, wo gaey aur is mein gir gaey, phir hamari taraf wapis aaye to unki wo kharabi khatam ho chuki thi aur wo khoobsurat ban gaey they.'' aur hadees ke in zayed alfaz mein farmaya : ''wahan wo taweel aadmi jo baagh mein tha wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) they, aur wo bachchey jo unke ird-gird they, ye wo bachchey they jo deene fitrat par faut huey they.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : baaz musalmanon ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mushrikon ke bachchey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mushrikon ke bachchey bhi, aur log jin ka aadha dhad achchha aur aadha dhad qabeeh (badsurat) tha to ye log wo they jinhonne achhey amal bhi kiye they aur burey amal bhi, Allah ne unse darguzar farmaya.'' Bukhari."
4626,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se bada jhoot ye hai ke aadmi apni aakhon ko wo chiz dikhaye (yani jhoota khuwab bayan karey) jo unhoney nahin dekhi.'' Bukhari.
4627,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sehri (yani pichhli raat ke) waqt ka khuwab sach honey mein qarib tar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
